#Plot Random Effect of Country
lattice::dotplot(ranef(savemale_base, which = "Country", condVar = TRUE), scales = list(y = list(alternating = 0)))
## $Country

#IncomeGeo Interaction
income.geo.interaction.df <- as.data.frame(Effect(c("Income", "Geo"), savemale_geoint, xlevels = list(Income=seq(min(savemale$Income), max(savemale$Income), 0.1))))

ggplot(data = income.geo.interaction.df, aes(Income, fit, color=Geo), position=position_dodge(width=0.5)) +
  geom_line(aes(linetype = Geo), size = 2) + geom_ribbon(aes(ymin=lower, ymax=upper, fill=Geo), alpha = 0.3, colour=NA) + labs(title = 'Interaction: Income and Geography for Save Male Scenario', y = "Save Male", x = "Income") 

#AgeGeo Interaction
age.geo.interaction.df <- as.data.frame(Effect(c("Age", "Geo"), savemale_geoint, xlevels = list(Age=seq(min(savemale$Age), max(savemale$Age), 0.1))))

ggplot(data = age.geo.interaction.df, aes(Age, fit, color=Geo), position=position_dodge(width=0.5)) +
  geom_line(aes(linetype = Geo), size = 2) + geom_ribbon(aes(ymin=lower, ymax=upper, fill=Geo), alpha = 0.3, colour=NA) + labs(title = 'Interaction: Age and Geography for Save Male Scenario', y = "Save Male", x = "Age") 

#PoliticalLevel Interaction
pol.geo.interaction.df <- as.data.frame(Effect(c("Political_level", "Geo"), savemale_geoint, xlevels = list(Political_level=seq(min(savemale$Political_level), max(savemale$Political_level), 0.1))))

ggplot(data = pol.geo.interaction.df, aes(Political_level, fit, color=Geo), position=position_dodge(width=0.5)) +
  geom_line(aes(linetype = Geo), size = 2) + geom_ribbon(aes(ymin=lower, ymax=upper, fill=Geo), alpha = 0.3, colour=NA) + labs(title = 'Interaction: Political_Level and Geography for Save Male Scenario', y = "Save Male", x = "Political_Level") 

#Religious_Level Interaction
rel.geo.interaction.df <- as.data.frame(Effect(c("Religious_level", "Geo"), savemale_geoint, xlevels = list(Religious_level=seq(min(savemale$Religious_level), max(savemale$Religious_level), 0.1))))

ggplot(data = rel.geo.interaction.df, aes(Religious_level, fit, color=Geo), position=position_dodge(width=0.5)) + geom_line(aes(linetype = Geo), size = 2) + geom_ribbon(aes(ymin=lower, ymax=upper, fill=Geo), alpha = 0.3, colour=NA) + labs(title = 'Interaction: Religious_Level and Geography for Save Male Scenario', y = "Save Male", x = "Religious_Level") 

#Gender Interaction

gender.geo.interaction.df <- as.data.frame(Effect(c("Gender", "Geo"), savemale_geoint))

ggplot(data = gender.geo.interaction.df, aes(Gender, fit, group=Geo)) + geom_point(aes(shape = Geo, color = Geo, size =1), position=position_dodge(width=0.5)) + geom_errorbar(aes(ymin=upper, ymax=lower), width = 0.4, position=position_dodge(width=0.5)) + labs(title = 'Interaction between Gender and Geographic Regions for Save Male Scenario', y = "Save Male", x = "Gender") 

#Education Interaction

education.geo.interaction.df <- as.data.frame(Effect(c("Education", "Geo"), savemale_geoint))

ggplot(data = education.geo.interaction.df, aes(Education, fit, group=Geo)) + geom_point(aes(shape = Geo, color = Geo, size =1), position=position_dodge(width=0.5)) + geom_errorbar(aes(ymin=upper, ymax=lower), width = 0.4, position=position_dodge(width=0.5)) + labs(title = 'Interaction between Education and Geographic Regions for Save Male Scenario', y = "Save Male", x = "Education")
